<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Login Successful</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 30px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      h4 {
        color: #34495e;
      }
      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .details {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }
      .details p {
        margin: 4px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
      <p>
        We noticed a successful login to your account just now.
      </p>

      <div class="details">
        <p style="text-align: center; color: #2c3e50;"><strong>Login Details</strong></p>
        <p><strong>Date & Time:</strong> <%= date %></p>
        <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> <%= ip || 'N/A' %></p>
        <p><strong>Device:</strong> <%= device || 'N/A' %></p>
        <p><strong>Operating System:</strong> <%= os || 'N/A' %></p>
        <p><strong>Browser:</strong> <%= browser || 'N/A' %></p>
      </div>

      <p>
        If this was you, no further action is needed. If you did not initiate this login,
        please secure your account immediately.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you for using our service!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br />The Rental House Management Team</p>

      <div class="footer">
        Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Rental House Management System
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
